      <title>英国监管机构计划扩大 ESG 投资监管范围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/uk-regulator-plans-to-broaden-scope-of-esg-investing-regulations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国金融行为监管局正计划将其 ESG 投资规则的范围从基金管理扩大到更广泛的投资组合，包括专注于私人和财富市场的投资组合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-23/uk-regulator-plans-to-broaden-scope-of-esg-investing-regulations</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 14:10:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
